**Dimension:** Cognitive Readability
**Lint:** clippy::option_if_let_else

## Violation
`if let Some(x) = opt { f(x) } else { g() }` is more concisely `opt.map_or_else(g, f)`.

## Locations
- src/modes/mod.rs: 379, 398
- src/pipeline.rs: 225, 854

## Mandated Refactor
```rust
// Before
let v = if let Some(x) = opt { compute(x) } else { default() };
// After
let v = opt.map_or_else(|| default(), compute);
// Or for a plain value default: opt.map_or(default_value, compute);
```
